    "description": "<strong>Enter the Arena</strong><br>Join a game, fight other players as a squad and become the true champion. Slay the enemy using incredible traversal abilities, a set of customizable spells and the surrounding environment. For every victory, you will receive rewards that help you become even stronger. Will you rise to the challenge and become worthy?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855300/extras/b1ca41f8a72fc2875879c35470dcc607.poster.avif?t=1756902324\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855300/extras/b1ca41f8a72fc2875879c35470dcc607.webm?t=1756902324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855300/extras/b1ca41f8a72fc2875879c35470dcc607.mp4?t=1756902324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Make your own choices</strong><br>Create your own character build by choosing from a whole arsenal of weapons, equipment, spells and talents to stay ahead of the competition!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855300/extras/723f61c24d87674b8659c8cb683dafcf.poster.avif?t=1756902324\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855300/extras/723f61c24d87674b8659c8cb683dafcf.webm?t=1756902324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855300/extras/723f61c24d87674b8659c8cb683dafcf.mp4?t=1756902324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Descend into the depths</strong><br>Join forces with other players and embark on expeditions into the unknown as you explore a procedurally generated underworld. Fight hordes of terrifying creatures, overcome deadly traps and defeat powerful bosses to claim the riches waiting in its depths. But beware: Rival raiding parties won’t stop at anything to take the loot for themselves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855300/extras/273088d845a8695ba62598686a3bef0b.poster.avif?t=1756902324\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855300/extras/273088d845a8695ba62598686a3bef0b.webm?t=1756902324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855300/extras/273088d845a8695ba62598686a3bef0b.mp4?t=1756902324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Welcome to Abaddon</strong><br>Your story begins in Abaddon, a city shaped by magic and ruled by eternal laws. Legends say it was built by the gods, but what you will find here is all too human. Get rich beyond your wildest dreams, fight for honor, glory and fame and become more powerful than any mortal before you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855300/extras/c5c9d46b699d7c6bd08bfc4e53e134c8.poster.avif?t=1756902324\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855300/extras/c5c9d46b699d7c6bd08bfc4e53e134c8.webm?t=1756902324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855300/extras/c5c9d46b699d7c6bd08bfc4e53e134c8.mp4?t=1756902324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
